textAnnotations.description:
Aragorn, Company Leader
Legendary Creature – Human Ranger
Whenever the Ring tempts you, if you chose
a creature other than Aragorn, Company
Leader as your Ring-bearer, put your choice
of a counter from among first strike, vigilance,
deathtouch, and lifelink on Aragorn.
Whenever you put one or more counters on
Aragorn, put one of each of those kinds of
counters on up to one other target creature.
R 0191
LTR EN ANNA STEINBAUER
3/3
ⒸMEE
